
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Payments";
    Layout = "~/Views/Shared/_Layout.cshtml";
}

<div class="container">
    <div class="row text-center">
        <h2>Payments</h2>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="container">
    <div class="panel-group" id="accordion">
        <div class="panel panel-default">
            <div class="panel-heading">
                <h4 class="panel-title">
                    <a class="accordion-toggle collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseTwelve">Paying with PayPal</a>
                </h4>
            </div>
            <div id="collapseTwelve" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                <div class="panel-body">
                    <p>PayPal payments are usually credited within a few minutes.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="panel panel-default">
            <div class="panel-heading">
                <h4 class="panel-title">
                    <a class="accordion-toggle collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseThirteen">What sort of payment confirmation will I receive?</a>
                </h4>
            </div>
            <div id="collapseThirteen" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                <div class="panel-body">
                    <p>You will receive an order confirmation which contains the link to your PayPal payment.</p>
                    <p>If for some reason, the payment process is interrupted, this link offers you the chance to reprocess your payment with PayPal. Please note, however, that after three hours payment via PayPal is no longer possible.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="panel panel-default">
            <div class="panel-heading">
                <h4 class="panel-title">
                    <a class="accordion-toggle collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseFourteen">Can I pay by PayPal without creating a PayPal account?</a>
                </h4>
            </div>
            <div id="collapseFourteen" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                <div class="panel-body">
                    <p>Yes, in order to do so select PayPal as your preferred payment method during checkout. At the end of the ordering process, you will be directed to PayPal. If you prefer not to create an account, then simply select the option ‘Don’t have a PayPal account?’ and you can enter your card details and confirm the payment as a PayPal guest.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="panel panel-default">
            <div class="panel-heading">
                <h4 class="panel-title">
                    <a class="accordion-toggle collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseFifteen">What happens if I make a return when I payed with PayPal?</a>
                </h4>
            </div>
            <div id="collapseFifteen" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                <div class="panel-body">
                    <p>The amount will be credited to your PayPal account, unless you have paid as a guest. In that case, the amount will be credited to your bank account.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>